cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CY

This paper involves natural language processing and artificial intelligence to develop an automated orthodontic diagnostic system. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing. The paper also involves machine learning and data analysis, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with information retrieval and ranking, which falls under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper involves the use of technology in the medical field, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
